{"tid":2362619,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"記者質疑演辭冇提三權分立 張舉能：變咗好政治化，唔適合評論","createTime":"2021-01-11T14:34:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-11T15:44:26.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"cad863454d4036d407a5f439d52faedee918d70a","tid":2362619,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T14:34:28.000Z","msg":"（獨媒報導）司法機構下午進行法律年度開啟典禮，新任終審法院首席法官張舉能在典禮後見記者。有記者問到三權分立的問題，質疑張舉能在演辭中竟沒有提及，張舉能稱，「三權分立屬好熱門問題，變咗好政治化，我唔適合喺呢方面評論。」他認為，最重要的是《基本法》第2、19和85條中均提到，司法機構可獨立行使權利判案，「司法獨立、獨立判案，呢個係最主要、最重要關心嘅事情。」<br />\n<br />\n記者又問到，法庭無可避免處理政治案件，壓力是否相應增加。張舉能表示，所有工作均有壓力，法官判案的結果難以令所有人開心滿意，「有批評、有唔開心，呢個係工作預咗一部分，係在所難免，法官有專業處理壓力。」<br />\n<br />\n被問到上任後的最大挑戰，張舉能大耍太極，表示人人都面對挑戰，再次重複開幕典禮演辭中，曾提及的司法機構三項致力維持的基本要點。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1080146\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1080146&d=bDhD0m8o4fsrNJ%2BdslRS%2BQvpIPIfgcH1aomtamkqoQA%3D&h=bbeb51c8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1080146&h=2c841132\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1080146</a>"},{"pid":"412d98c5b010b29fc4311583f86b4bb26c41bd00","tid":2362619,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T14:36:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0144a9c2f93adb339013af47d207b060047d9784","tid":2362619,"uid":167931,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T14:37:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c94d3d9bb187a3a8d25033ddaf3fc5cc47c00481","tid":2362619,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T14:37:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/